---
// Hero Servicios - Sección hero para página Servicios
---

<section class="relative min-h-[65vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-black pt-32 md:pt-36 lg:pt-44">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/imagenes/imagen3.webp" alt="Servicios Industriales" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 via-black/30 to-black/60"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 15px, rgba(170, 126, 86, 0.08) 15px, rgba(170, 126, 86, 0.08) 30px);"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10 xl:px-12 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center text-white" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.7), 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-xs md:text-sm mb-6 opacity-90 tracking-wide">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-golden-light transition-colors font-medium">Inicio</a>
        <span class="mx-3">•</span>
        <span class="text-golden-light font-semibold">Servicios</span>
      </nav>
      
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-display); letter-spacing: 0.03em;" class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-normal mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
        Nuestros Servicios
      </h1>
      
      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body);" class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light">
        Soluciones integrales en reparación, mantenimiento preventivo y correctivo 
        de sopladores industriales con servicio técnico especializado.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Service highlights -->
      <div style="font-family: var(--font-heading);" class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6 text-sm md:text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full backdrop-blur">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-golden-light rounded-full"></div>
          <span>Reparación Integral</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full backdrop-blur">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-golden rounded-full"></div>
          <span>Mantenimiento Preventivo</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full backdrop-blur">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-rust rounded-full"></div>
          <span>Servicio Correctivo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-16 left-16 w-20 h-20 border border-golden/30 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-16 right-16 w-28 h-28 border border-golden-light/20 rounded-full animate-pulse delay-1000"></div>

  <!-- Golden bottom separator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-[3px]" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, #aa7e56 30%, #cca373 60%, #aa7e56 80%, transparent 100%);"></div>
</section>